title._content: Rugged Terrain Typical of Coastal Mountains Fronting on Prince William Sound...08/1974

description._content: Original Caption: Rugged Terrain Typical of Coastal Mountains Fronting on Prince William Sound. A Glacial Tarn Appears as an Emerald Green Lake at the Upper Left on the Mountainside in Contrast with the Blue Waters of the Pacific in the Foreground.
